<section id=\"city-hero\" class=\"city-hero-section \"><div class=\"section-shell city-hero-shell\"><div class=\"city-hero-copy\"><div class=\"hero-breadcrumbs\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><span>Dog Parks Directory</span><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><strong>Brick Township</strong></div><p class=\"hero-eyebrow\">City spotlight</p><h1>Dog Parks in Brick Township, NJ</h1><p class=\"hero-description\">Discover 31 dog-friendly spots in Brick Township, NJ.</p><div class=\"hero-cta-row\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta primary\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-check\"></i>Browse directory</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta ghost\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i>Open map</button><a class=\"hero-cta text-link\" href=\"/list-your-park\"><i class=\"bi bi-plus-circle\"></i>Submit a park</a></div><div class=\"hero-footnotes\"><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Data refreshed weekly</span><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Live availability coming soon</span></div></div><div class=\"city-hero-visual\"><div class=\"hero-image-card\"><img alt=\"Brick Township dog park landscape\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/brick-township/hero.webp\"/><div class=\"hero-image-gradient\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"city-premium-section\" aria-labelledby=\"city-premium-heading\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"city-premium-header\"><div><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Premium spotlight</span><h2 id=\"city-premium-heading\">Premium parks in <!-- -->Brick Township</h2><p>Partners highlighted here are currently investing in featured placement across this guide.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-header-actions\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">Feature my park</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to sales</a></div></div><div class