tyle=\"font-size:0.75rem\" class=\"jsx-2b2fd5f238fe2f81 bi bi-star-fill\"></i>4.9</div></td><td style=\"padding:20px 12px;color:#475569;font-size:0.875rem\" class=\"jsx-2b2fd5f238fe2f81\">Dog Park</td><td style=\"padding:20px 12px;color:#475569;font-size:0.875rem\" class=\"jsx-2b2fd5f238fe2f81\">Fenced Run</td><td style=\"padding:20px 12px;color:#059669;font-weight:600\" class=\"jsx-2b2fd5f238fe2f81\">—</td><td style=\"padding:20px 12px\" class=\"jsx-2b2fd5f238fe2f81\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:999px;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;background:#f1f5f9;color:#475569\" class=\"jsx-2b2fd5f238fe2f81\">Community Favorite</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div></section><section id=\"park-collections\" class=\"park-collections-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Curated collections</span><h2>Choose the vibe that fits your next outing</h2><p>Segmented park groupings built from live data so you can jump straight to the experiences that matter most.</p></div><div class=\"park-type-guide-wrapper\"><section id=\"park-types-guide\" class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d park-types-guide-section\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d collection-cards-grid\"><article class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d collection-guide-card \"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-header\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-header-top\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d spots-pill\">31<!-- --> spots</span><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-rating\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-star-fill\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">4.5<!-- --> avg</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-type-info\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d type-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-tree-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\"><h3 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Dog Park</h3><p class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d short-description\">Traditional outdoor off‑leash areas and fenced runs, optimized for everyday exercise.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-content \"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">What is it?</h4><p class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Traditional outdoor off-leash areas where dogs can run freely and socialize with other dogs.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Key Features</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d features-chips\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Fenced enclosures</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Open grass areas</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Agility equipment</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Water stations</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Waste disposal</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Best For</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-list\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">High-energy dogs</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Social dogs</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Owners looking for free exercise options</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">What to Bring</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-list\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Leash (for entering/exiting)</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Water bowl</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Waste bags</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Toys</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Treats</span></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Pro Tips</h4><ul class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d tips-list\"><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Check park rules before visiting</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Keep your dog&#x27;s vaccinations up to date</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Supervise your dog at all times</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Clean up after your dog immediately</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Respect other dogs and owners</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-footer\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d expand-toggle\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">View guide</span><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></button><a class=\"jump-link\" href=\"#dog-park-parks\">Jump to list<i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-arrow-right\"></i></a></div></article></div></section></div></div></section><section id=\"map-and-neighborhoods\" class=\"map-experience-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Interactive planning</span><h2>See everything laid out on the map</h2><p>Use the live map to lock in nearby options, preview ratings, and save time hopping between neighborhoods.</p></div><div class=\"map-grid\"><div class=\"map-panel\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><div style=\"min-height:320px;background:#f3f4f6\"></div><!--/$--></div><div class=\"map-sidebar\"><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Quick filters</h3><div class=\"map-chip-grid\"><button type=\"button\"><span>Dog Park</span><small>31</small></button></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Highest-rated nearby</h3><div class=\"mini-park-list\"><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Cody&#x27;s Canine Camp</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>5.0</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Stingray Tommy Dog Training and Boarding (since 1995)</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>5.0</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Wag Watchers Dog Boarding &amp; Pet Siting</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>5.0</strong></div></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card muted\"><p>Tip: tap any map marker to open directions, amenities, and current open hours.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"planning-essentials\" class=\"planning-essentials-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Visit toolkit</span><h2>Plan the perfect dog outing in <!-- -->Brick Township</h2><p>Borrow best practices from local trainers, rangers, and experienced pet parents.</p></div><div class=\"planning-grid\"><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h3>Peak &amp; quiet windows</h3><ul><li>6–9 AM: high energy social hour</li><li>10 AM–3 PM weekdays: calm training-friendly window</li><li>After 4 PM: sunset crowd + cooler temps</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-backpack\"></i></div><h3>Essentials checklist</h3><ul><li>Leash + harness for entry/exit control</li><li>Collapsible water bowl and fresh water</li><li>Plenty of waste bags and high-value treats</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-shield-check\"></i></div><h3>Local regulations</h3><ul><li>Keep proof of vaccinations or city license handy</li><li>Voice control required in most off-leash zones</li><li>Limit three dogs per handler in public parks</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-heart\"></i></div><h3>Community etiquette</h3><ul><li>Scan the park before entering and remove prong collars</li><li>Monitor play styles and intervene early</li><li>Share shaded space and refill water when you&#x27;re done</li></ul></article></div></div></section><section id=\"owner-cta\" class=\"owner-cta-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Partner with us</span><h2>Feature your Brick Township dog park</h2><p>Upgrade to a featured listing, share live availability, or pitch a new indoor concept. Our team drives qualified local pet parents every week.</p><div class=\"hero-cta-row\" style=\"margin-top:24px\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List a property</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Contact the team</a></div></div></section><section id=\"park-directory\" class=\"park-directory-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">City directory</span><h2>All dog parks in <!-- -->Brick Township</h2><p>Filter-ready cards with ratings, amenities, and quick actions. Use the chips to jump between sections.</p></div><div class=\"category-chip-row\"><button type=\"button\">Dog Park</button></div><div id=\"dog-park-parks\" class=\"directory-category\"><div class=\"directory-header\"><div><h3>Dog Park<!-- -->s<!-- --> in <!-- -->Brick Township</h3><p>31<!-- --> locations ·<!-- --> <!-- -->4.5<!-- --> <!-- -->average rating</p></div><span class=\"directory-count\">31</span></div><div class=\"directory-grid\"><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/88-pet-world\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">88 Pet World</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>4</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 10:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Brick Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">88 Pet World has become a favorite among the area residents.  What makes this pet store special is its safe, great. safe environment for my puppy Located in a safe area, This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (732) 899-1920. Visit their website at http://88petworld.net/ to learn more about their services and pricing.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/a-beautiful-dog-pet-salon\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">A Beautiful Dog Pet Salon</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 10:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Brick Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">For years, A Beautiful Dog Pet Salon has served as a steadfast anchor of the [Brick Township](/cities/brick-township-nj) community, earning its place as a beloved local institution. With a history of serving generations of tail-waggers, this location carries a sense of established trust and neighborhood pride that you can&#x27;t manufacture. Documented by 37 reviews and a 4.8-star legacy, it stands as a testament to the town&#x27;s enduring commitment to its animal residents.\n\nStepping into A Beautiful Dog Pet Salon feels like visiting an old friend. The facility balances traditional park values with modern maintenance standards, ensuring a timeless experience that feels both familiar and safe. It is more than just a plot of land; it is a repository of memories for families and a daily ritual for the neighborhood. For those who value consistency, heritage, and a strong sense of place, this Brick Township staple remains the gold standard.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](https://www.abeautifuldognj.com/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/a-wash-your-paws-a-grooming-salon-plus-self-service-dog-wash\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">A Wash Your Paws -a Grooming Salon plus self- service dog wash</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 9:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Brick Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Serious about your pup&#x27;s fitness and focus? A Wash Your Paws -a Grooming Salon plus self- service dog wash in [Brick Township](/cities/brick-township-nj) delivers a top-tier environment designed for activity and engagement. Rated 4.7 stars by a community of 177 disciplined dog owners, this facility is built on the logic of &quot;constructive play.&quot; It’s not just about running around; it’s about mental stimulation, clear boundaries, and a structured space where dogs can burn off energy productively.\n\nThe layout at A Wash Your Paws -a Grooming Salon plus self- service dog wash is ideal for training exercises, recall practice, and agility drills. The grounds are kept in peak condition to ensure safety during high-intensity play, and the respectful community of regulars understands the value of good canine etiquette. Whether you are working on commands or just need a reliable space for vigorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](http://www.washyourpaws.net/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/angela-hibbard-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Angela Hibbard Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 7:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Brick Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Serious about your pup&#x27;s fitness and focus? Angela Hibbard Park in [Brick Township](/cities/brick-township-nj) delivers a top-tier environment designed for activity and engagement. Rated 4.5 stars by a community of 282 disciplined dog owners, this facility is built on the logic of &quot;constructive play.&quot; It’s not just about running around; it’s about mental stimulation, clear boundaries, and a structured space where dogs can burn off energy productively.\n\nThe layout at Angela Hibbard Park is ideal for training exercises, recall practice, and agility drills. The grounds are kept in peak condition to ensure safety during high-intensity play, and the respectful community of regulars understands the value of good canine etiquette. Whether you are working on commands or just need a reliable space for vigorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](http://www.bricktownship.net/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/bay-harbor-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Bay Harbor Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">unknown</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Hours vary by season</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Brick Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">For years, Bay Harbor Park has served as a steadfast anchor of the [Brick Township](/cities/brick-township-nj) community, earning its place as a beloved local institution. With a history of serving generations of tail-waggers, this location carries a sense of established trust and neighborhood pride that you can&#x27;t manufacture. Documented by 65 reviews and a 4.7-star legacy, it stands as a testament to the town&#x27;s enduring commitment to its animal residents.\n\nStepping into Bay Harbor Park feels like visiting an old friend. The facility balances traditional park values with modern maintenance standards, ensuring a timeless experience that feels both familiar and safe. It is more than just a plot of land; it is a repository of memories for families and a daily ritual for the neighborhood. For those who value consistency, heritage, and a strong sense of place, this Brick Township staple remains the gold standard.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](https://www.bricknj.gov/business_detail_T29_R30.php) to learn more about their services and updated hours.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/brick-reservoir\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Brick Reservoir</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 6:30 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Brick Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">If you&#x27;re looking for the ultimate wag-worthy social hub in [Brick Township](/cities/brick-township-nj), look no further than Brick Reservoir. This vibrant community destination has earned a reputation as the &quot;place to be&quot; for local pet parents who want more than just a walk—they want a meetup. Boasting a solid 4.8-star rating from 374 reviews, the park radiates a welcoming energy where tails never stop wagging and neighbors become friends. Whether you&#x27;re there for a quick playdate or a long afternoon of socializing, the atmosphere is always buzzing with positivity.\n\nAt Brick Reservoir, the focus is on connection. The layout encourages interaction, making it easy for pups to find playmates while owners chat on the sidelines. It’s not just a facility; it’s a social pillar of the Brick Township scene, offering a safe, clean, and joyous environment where every visitor feels like a VIP. For a fun, friendly, and community-centered experience, this spot is a local favorite.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](http://brickmua.com/reservoir/resdirections.asp) to learn more about their services and updated hours.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/cody-s-canine-camp\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Cody&#x27;s Canine Camp</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\