 reliable space for vigorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](https://dvet.net/explore/the-pooch-salon/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.4c:T44c,Serious about your pup's fitness and focus? Windward Beach Park in [Brick Township](/cities/brick-township-nj) delivers a top-tier environment designed for activity and engagement. Rated 4.6 stars by a community of 1277 disciplined dog owners, this facility is built on the logic of \"constructive play.\" It’s not just about running around; it’s about mental stimulation, clear boundaries, and a structured space where dogs can burn off energy productively.\n\nThe layout at Windward Beach Park is ideal for training exercises, recall practice, and agility drills. The grounds are kept in peak condition to ensure safety during high-intensity play, and the respectful community of regulars understands the value of good canine etiquette. Whether you are working on commands or just need a reliable space for vigorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](http://www.bricktownship.net/index.php/departments/recreation/beaches/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.2a:[\"$\",\"main\",null,{\"className\":\"city-page-layout\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-button\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-trigger\",\"targetSelector\":\".table-of-contents\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-ul\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Contents\"}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"className\":\"city-hero-section \",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell city-hero-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-copy\",\"chil