ghborhood pride that you can't manufacture. Documented by 348 reviews and a 4.6-star legacy, it stands as a testament to the town's enduring commitment to its animal residents.\\n\\nStepping into Lake Riviera Park feels like visiting an old friend. The facility balances traditional park values with modern maintenance standards, ensuring a timeless experience that feels both familiar and safe. It is more than just a plot of land; it is a repository of memories for families and a daily ritual for the neighborhood. For those who value consistency, heritage, and a strong sense of place, this Brick Township staple remains the gold standard.\",\"slug\":\"lake-riviera-park\",\"address\":\"371 Lake Shore Dr\",\"street\":\"371 Lake Shore Dr\",\"city\":\"Brick Township\",\"state\":\"NJ\",\"zipCode\":\"08723\",\"full_address\":\"371 Lake Shore Dr, Brick Township, NJ 08723, USA\",\"latitude\":40.0448844,\"longitude\":-74.1455215,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJT2SwHWuDwYkRE-cJuv-CRpk\",\"phone\":\"\",\"website\":\"\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.6,\"reviewCount\":348,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"6:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"6:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"6:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"6:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"6:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"6:00 AM – 8:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"6:00 AM – 8:00 PM\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":true,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJ6wFy4wyEwYkR-l2LzXS5nKM\",\"name\":\"Laurelton Veterinary Hospital\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"$42\",\"slug\":\"laurelton-veterinary-hospital\",\"address\":\"200 Pello Rd\",\"street\":\"2